metadata.name: Hang Them High
metadata.description: Bury 'em Deep is a collection of 50 hand-drawn one of one art NFTs by NheFT. Bury 'em Deep is the beginning of an exploration into what can be accomplished with one of one art in the NFT space through collaboration, utility, and thematic elements. We are excited to begin this journey with you by releasing Bury 'em Deep. Team NHefT also looks forward to bringing you even more exciting one of one NFT content in the coming months and years. Thank you.
